'''卢克·约书亚·莱特洛'''（{{lang-en|Luke Joshua Letlow}}，{{bd|1979年|12月6日|2020年|12月29日|catIdx=Letlow}}<ref name=rollcall>{{cite web |url=https://rollcall.com/2020/12/05/luke-letlow-wins-runoff-to-succeed-his-boss-ralph-abraham-in-louisianas-5th-district/ |title=Luke Letlow Wins Runoff to Succeed His Boss, Ralph Abraham, in Louisiana’s 5th District |first=Stephanie |last=Akin |date=2020-12-05 |access-date=2020-12-30 |work=Roll Call |quote=... Letlow, who turns 41 on Sunday ...' |archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206034255/https://rollcall.com/2020/12/05/luke-letlow-wins-runoff-to-succeed-his-boss-ralph-abraham-in-louisianas-5th-district/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="WDSU Letlow dies">{{cite news |author=WDSU Digital Team |title=Congressman-elect Luke Letlow dies from COVID-19 |url=https://www.wdsu.com/article/sources-congressman-elect-luke-letlow-dies-from-covid-19/35093657# |publisher=WDSU |date=2020-12-30 |accessdate=2020-12-30 |language=en |quote=The following statement was issued by [Andrew] Bautsch: 'Congressman-elect Luke Letlow, 41, passed away this evening at Ochsner-LSU Health Shreveport due to complications from COVID-19.' |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025006/https://www.wdsu.com/article/sources-congressman-elect-luke-letlow-dies-from-covid-19/35093657 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是一位来自[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的美国政治家。2020年，他以[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]]人的身份参选并当选为{{le|路易斯安那州第五国会选区|Louisiana's 5th congressional district}}的[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]议员，但在上任前死于[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]并发症。在当选国会议员之前，莱特洛曾担任即将退休的众议员[[拉尔夫·亚伯拉罕|拉尔夫·亚伯拉罕]]的[[幕僚长|幕僚长]]。

==早年生活和教育==
卢克·莱特洛在[[门罗_(路易斯安那州)|门罗]]西边的{{le|斯达特 (路易斯安那州)|Start, Louisiana|斯达特}}农村[[非建制地区|非建制地区]]长大，毕业于{{le|瓦希塔基督教高中|Ouachita Christian High School}}，并于2003年在[[路易斯安那理工大学|路易斯安那理工大学]]获得计算机信息系统[[理学学士|理学学士]]学位<ref name="engagement"/>。在路易斯安那理工大学读书时，莱特洛曾于2000年在{{le|约翰·库克西|John Cooksey}}手下实习，当时库克西在[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]代表{{le|路易斯安那州第五国会选区|Louisiana's 5th congressional district}}<ref name="newsstar">{{cite web|url=https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/2020/03/09/luke-letlow-joins-congressional-race-ralph-abrahams-backing/4998583002/|title=Luke Letlow joins congressional race with Ralph Abraham's backing|last1=Hilburn|first1=Greg|work=The News-Star|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105024957/https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/2020/03/09/luke-letlow-joins-congressional-race-ralph-abrahams-backing/4998583002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他曾在2001年担任路易斯安那理工{{le|大学共和党人|College Republicans}}主席，2002年担任路易斯安那州大学共和党人联合会主席<ref name="engagement">{{Cite news|date=2013-03-24|title=Engagements - Luke Letlow and Julia Barnhill|pages=44|work=The News-Star|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/10019641/engagements-luke-letlow-and-julia/|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105024959/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/10019641/engagements-luke-letlow-and-julia/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="newsstar"/><ref name=richland/>。

==职业==
莱特洛在2005年至2008年[[鲍比·金达尔|鲍比·金达尔]]担任[[路易斯安那州第一国会选区|路易斯安那州第一国会选区]]美国众议院议员期间为其工作，并在2008年至2010年金达尔担任{{le|路易斯安那州州长列表|List of governors of Louisiana|路易斯安那州州长}}的第一个任期内担任政府间事务主任<ref>{{cite web |author=groberts |url=https://www.theadvocate.com/baton_rouge/news/politics/article_63c230a2-5336-524d-bc44-624cd82c55cf.html |title=Newly elected Congressman Ralph Abraham names chief of staff for U.S. House office in DC | State Politics |work=The Advocate |date=2014-12-10 |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025002/https://www.theadvocate.com/baton_rouge/news/politics/article_63c230a2-5336-524d-bc44-624cd82c55cf.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后，他在[[丹佛|丹佛]]的一家能源公司QEP资源公司担任政府和社区事务总监<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/local/2014/12/10/letlow-named-abrahams-chief-staff/20201499/ |title=Letlow named Abraham’s chief of staff |publisher=Thenewsstar.com |date=2014-12-10 |access-date=2020-12-06 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105024959/https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/local/2014/12/10/letlow-named-abrahams-chief-staff/20201499/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rollcall.com/2020/12/05/luke-letlow-wins-runoff-to-succeed-his-boss-ralph-abraham-in-louisianas-5th-district/ |title=Luke Letlow wins runoff to succeed his boss, Rep. Ralph Abraham |publisher=Rollcall.com |access-date=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025000/https://www.rollcall.com/2020/12/05/luke-letlow-wins-runoff-to-succeed-his-boss-ralph-abraham-in-louisianas-5th-district/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，莱特洛回到路易斯安那州，在[[拉尔夫·亚伯拉罕|拉尔夫·亚伯拉罕]]{{le|2014年路易斯安那州美国众议院选举|2014 United States House of Representatives elections in Louisiana|竞选}}路易斯安那州第五国会选区期间担任其竞选经理<ref name=newsstar/>。他在亚伯拉罕三届任期内担任其[[幕僚长|幕僚长]]<ref name=richland/>。

2020年3月9日，在亚伯拉罕履行了他不超过三届任期的承诺后，莱特洛宣布参选<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=Hilburn|first=Greg|date=2020-12-29|title=Louisiana Congressman-elect Luke Letlow dies with COVID-19|url=https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/2020/12/29/louisiana-congressman-elect-luke-letlow-dies-covid/4082977001/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025033/https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/2020/12/29/louisiana-congressman-elect-luke-letlow-dies-covid/4082977001/|archive-date=2021-01-05|access-date=2020-12-30|website=The News-Star}}</ref>。亚伯拉罕在莱特洛宣布参选的同时公开支持他<ref name=richland>{{cite web|url=https://www.richlandtoday.com/start-resident-seeks-congressional-seat|title=Start resident seeks Congressional seat|work=Richland Beacon-News|location=Rayville, Louisiana|date=2020-03-17|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025041/https://www.richlandtoday.com/start-resident-seeks-congressional-seat|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在11月3日的不分党派全面初选中，莱特洛以33%的得票率获得第一名，而共和党同僚、州众议员{{le|兰斯·哈里斯|Lance Harris}}以17%的得票率位居第二<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/2020/11/03/luke-letlow-lance-harris-emerge-all-republican-runoff-5th-congressional-district/6058832002/|title=Luke Letlow, Lance Harris emerge in all-Republican runoff for 5th Congressional District|first=Greg|last=Hilburn|work=Monroe News-Star|date=2020-11-03|accessdate=2020-12-29|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025044/https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/2020/11/03/luke-letlow-lance-harris-emerge-all-republican-runoff-5th-congressional-district/6058832002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。莱特洛以62%的得票率赢得了12月5日的[[两轮选举制|决选]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Louisiana election results: Letlow, Harris in GOP runoff for Congress|url=https://www.houmatoday.com/story/news/2020/11/03/luke-letlow-lance-harris-emerge-all-republican-runoff-5th-congressional-district/6058832002/|access-date=2020-12-30|work=Houma Todaym|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025039/https://www.houmatoday.com/story/news/2020/11/03/luke-letlow-lance-harris-emerge-all-republican-runoff-5th-congressional-district/6058832002/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/2020/12/05/luke-letlow-wins-louisianas-5th-congressional-district-race/3822036001/|title=Luke Letlow wins Louisiana's 5th Congressional District race|date=2020-12-05|last1=Hilburn|first1=Greg|work=The News-Star|access-date=2020-12-30|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025046/https://www.thenewsstar.com/story/news/2020/12/05/luke-letlow-wins-louisianas-5th-congressional-district-race/3822036001/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==个人生活和死亡==
莱特洛和妻子[[朱莉娅·莱特洛|朱莉娅]]以及他们的两个孩子住在[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]的{{le|斯达特 (路易斯安那州)|Start, Louisiana|斯达特}}。<ref name=richland/>

2020年12月18日，在[[COVID-19大流行|COVID-19大流行]]期间，莱特洛宣布他对病毒检测呈阳性。他在门罗住院<ref name=pol1>{{Cite web|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/12/29/luke-letlow-covid-congress-452218|title=Louisiana congressman-elect dies of Covid|first=Melanie|last=Zanona|website=Politico|date=2020-12-29|accessdate=2020-12-30|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230030047/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/12/29/luke-letlow-covid-congress-452218|dead-url=no}}</ref>。病情恶化后，他于12月23日被转移到{{le|路易斯安那州立大学健康科学中心什里夫波特|LSU Health Sciences Center Shreveport}}的[[重症监护室|重症监护室]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Letlow transferred to ICU for COVID-19 treatment |url=https://apnews.com/article/louisiana-coronavirus-pandemic-shreveport-c528a367318c0335f6b43f7a3dc2e5ce |access-date=2020-12-30 |work=Associated Press |date=2020-12-23 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025047/https://apnews.com/article/louisiana-coronavirus-pandemic-shreveport-c528a367318c0335f6b43f7a3dc2e5ce |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月29日，莱特洛死于COVID-19并发症，享年41岁，距离他计划宣誓就职的日期仅有5天<ref name="WDSU Letlow dies"/><ref name=pol1/>。医院报告称，他入院时没有任何潜在疾病，但在一次手术后死于心脏病发作<ref name=":0" />。

路易斯安那州州长{{le|约翰·贝尔·爱德华兹 |John Bel Edwards}}下令，在莱特洛葬礼当天，该州将降半旗向其致哀<ref>{{cite news |last=WAFB |first=Staff |url=https://www.wafb.com/2020/12/29/report-louisiana-congressman-elect-luke-letlow-dies-after-being-hospitalized-with-coronavirus/ |title=Louisiana Congressman-elect Luke Letlow dies after being hospitalized with coronavirus |work=WAFB News |date=2020-12-29 |accessdate=2020-12-30 |archive-date=2021-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025047/https://www.wafb.com/2020/12/29/report-louisiana-congressman-elect-luke-letlow-dies-after-being-hospitalized-with-coronavirus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他还计划在2021年3月20日举行{{le|2021年路易斯安那州第五国会选区特别选举|2021 Louisiana's 5th congressional district special election|特别选举}}，以填补莱特洛的空缺，如果需要，将在4月进行决选<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theadvocate.com/baton_rouge/news/politics/elections/article_2d694272-4ab9-11eb-a71e-7361c76300dc.html|title=Election to replace Luke Letlow in Congress to be set for March, officials say|work=The Advocate|first=Sam|last=Karlin|date=2020-12-30|accessdate=2020-12-31|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105025047/https://www.theadvocate.com/baton_rouge/news/politics/elections/article_2d694272-4ab9-11eb-a71e-7361c76300dc.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當天，該特別選舉由盧克遺孀朱莉婭勝選。

